title: Grateful Dead Live at The Palladium on 1977-05-03
description:
Set 1

Promised Land, Bertha, Me & My Uncle, Peggy-O, Jack Straw, Row Jimmy, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication, Deal, Good Lovin', Ship of Fools, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Might As Well, Estimated Prophet, Sugaree, Samson & Delilah, Friend Of The Devil, Eyes Of The World-> Wharf Rat-> Not Fade Away-> Around & Around, E: Uncle John's Band
